What are you doing?

20
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,960
What right do you have to stop me?

21
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,470
What...

22
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:11,910
What right do you have to arrest me?

23
00:02:11,910 --> 00:02:12,400
Let go!

24
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,000
Hold him down!

25
