85
00:04:06,630 --> 00:04:07,560
Who are you?

86
00:04:07,710 --> 00:04:08,970
Where do you come from?

87
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:09,910
Well,

88
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,400
I can't tell you.

89
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,260
What do you want

90
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:13,150
in Lucheng?

91
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:16,630
Even if I told you,

92
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,380
you wouldn't understand.

93
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,570
She's questioning you,

94
