release you easily.

115
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:12,830
Take him away.

116
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:13,560
Yes.

117
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:17,000
Move.

118
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,190
This hairpin

119
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:25,280
is enough to feed him
in prison for a lifetime.

120
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:29,240
I hope he's not some noble's son

121
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:31,310
coming here to make fun of us.

122
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,560
Inform the warden

123
