227
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:33,670
Can you just shut up

228
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,240
and be quiet for a moment?

229
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:55,210
When will your companions

230
00:10:55,370 --> 00:10:56,560
come to rescue you?

231
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,880
Brother Chen,

232
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:14,390
