233
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:15,270
Shouldn't we

234
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:16,870
be more cautious and keep a low profile?

235
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:17,550
Indeed,

236
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:18,840
the Jin people are vigilant.

237
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:21,030
