careful planning today,

238
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:23,390
deliberately having Wu
expose himself at the city gate

239
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,720
to distract the guards,

240
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:25,630
I'm afraid

241
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,640
