Let's stay calm first,

256
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:57,090
and continue our investigation in Lucheng.

257
00:11:57,630 --> 00:11:58,390
That day,

258
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,870
just after we left,

259
