Zang Budu was murdered.

260
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:03,480
It seems

261
00:12:04,190 --> 00:12:05,550
we're getting closer to Prince Annan

262
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:06,820
than ever before.

263
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:13,240
What nonsense are you talking about?

264
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,550
In front of me,

265
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:21,310
why do you still pretend?

266
00:12:21,810 --> 00:12:24,240
I've been following you
all the way from Ninglan.

267
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,630
When I saw you were in trouble,

268
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:27,490
I didn't care about anything else

269
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:28,440
and followed you

270
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:29,750
onto the prison cart.

271
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,360
