waste my memory-erasing pill.

282
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:24,790
Sleep now,

283
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:27,520
and when you wake up,
you won't remember me.

284
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,380
Since that's the case,

285
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:38,930
I'll have to go out
and search more carefully.

286
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,080
Besides,

